    "2. Jika count > 0 → DELETE FROM stock_summary WHERE date = '2026-06-05'\n",
    "3. INSERT data baru\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Data untuk tanggal tertentu **selalu fresh** (data terbaru menggantikan data lama)."
   ]
