    "\n",
    "## Cell [10] — Menjalankan Pipeline\n",
    "\n",
    "### Penjelasan\n",
    "\n",
    "Cell ini menjalankan seluruh pipeline ETL secara berurutan:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **LOG START** → Catat status `running`\n",
    "2. **EXTRACT** → Ambil data dari API IDX\n",
    "3. **TRANSFORM** → Bersihkan data\n",
    "4. **LOAD** → Simpan ke database\n",
    "5. **CLEANUP** → Hapus data lama\n",
    "6. **LOG RESULT** → Catat hasil akhir"
   ]
  },
